
About:
- Collect package information from __setup__(__plugin__)/__init__.py files in each package.
- Generate eggs to path
- Generate setup.py files used for pypi upload
- Publish package to pypi (requires auth)


Usage:
distribution.py --location [path] 
				--location [path] --components (Deploy only components from ally-py)
				--location [path] --plugins (Deploy only plugins from ally-py)
				

pip-3.2 install --target /opt/superdesk/ 
